high_descs: Turn to your left and go to the refrigerator, then turn right and go to the counter top just past the refrigerator, on your left.
Pick up the butter knife between the bread and the lettuce, on the counter top.
Move over to the left side of the counter.
Cut the head of lettuce closest to you, into slices.
Move back over to the right side of the counter top.
Place the knife back on the counter top, between the lettuce and the bread.
Move back over to the left side of the counter top.
Pick up on of the lettuce slices.
Go to the refrigerator to your left.
Place the slice of lettuce to the right of the plate, on the second shelf of the refrigerator, wait a moment for the lettuce to chill, then remove the lettuce from the refrigerator.
Turn around and go to the garbage bin on the floor, next to the kitchen island.
Place the lettuce in the garbage bin on the floor.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold slice of lettuce in the garbage bin.

high_descs: turn to the left and move forward to the fridge and turn right, move to the counter that is to the right of the fridge and turn left to face the counter
pick up the butter knife that is sitting on the counter to the right of two heads of lettuce
move slightly to the left facing the two heads of lettuce
use the knife to cut the head of lettuce in the front
move to the right of the counter slightly
put the knife on to the counter to the right of the heads of lettuce
move back to the left slightly to face both heads of lettuce
pick up a slice of the cut lettuce from the counter
move to the left to face the fridge
open the door of the fridge, put the lettuce slice on the top shelf, close the door to chill for a few seconds, open the door, remove the slice and close the door
turn around and move forward to the black trash can at the end of the counter of the left,  turn to face the trash can
put the slice of lettuce in to the trash can
anns.task_desc: put a chilled slice of lettuce in to the trash can

high_descs: Turn left then right and face the counter with the lettuce on your left.
Take the knife from the counter in front of you.
Turn left and face the counter on your right.
Slice the lettuce in front of you.
Turn right then face the counter to your left.
Place the knife on the counter in front of you.
Turn left then face the counter on your right.
Take a slice of lettuce from the counter in front of you.
Turn left and face the fridge to your right.
Place the lettuce in the fridge for a bit then take it out.
Turn around and face the black bin on your left.
Place lettuce in black bin in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place cold lettuce in black bin.
